#   Host SSH: tuo-server.com
#   Porta SSH: 2222
#   Username SSH: pilotpro
#   Password SSH: ssh_secure_password_2025
#   
#   Database (via tunnel):
#   Host: localhost
#   Porta: 15432
#   Database: n8n_mcp
